title: Bright Eyes - FLAC
description:
This torrent includes two of Bright Eyes&#039; albums, namely "Lifted (Or the Story Is in the Soil, Keep Your Ear to the Ground)" and "Digital Ashes in a Digital Urn"  Both were copied securely using EAC Exact Audio Copy V0.99 prebeta 3 with AccurateRip and later analysed with AuCDTect 0.8.2 to verify that the source was truly lossless.  Then the files were compressed with FLAC.  No failures were found on any level.  Properly researched and grammar-checked tags are included, along with embedded album covers and ReplayGain information.

These FLACs were encoded with version 1.2.1 on Linux by using parameters "-wVmep -b 2048 -l 12 -r &#039;0,8&#039; --delete-input-file --no-ogg *.wav".
